  description="Stop wasting budgets on short-term tactics. Our 90-day framework helps CMOs balance brand building with activation using marketing science + AI. 60/40 long/short. Mental availability at scale. Measurable ROMI. Evidence-based strategy for serious marketers."
  showHeader={true}
