      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-red-600 mb-2">95/5</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-red-900 mb-2">Short vs Long Split</p>
          <p class="text-red-700 text-sm">Most marketers spend 95% on activation, 5% on brand. Evidence shows 60/40 drives sustainable growth.</p>
        </div>

