          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-orange-600 mb-2">46%</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-orange-900 mb-2">Wasted Ad Spend</p>
          <p class="text-orange-700 text-sm">Nearly half of advertising fails to build mental availability or distinctive brand assets—it's just noise</p>
