        <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-yellow-600 mb-2">83%</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-yellow-900 mb-2">Focus on Short-Term</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Marketers prioritize immediate conversions over long-term brand building that compounds over years</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-500 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-3xl font-black text-purple-600 mb-2">12-24mo</div>
          <p class="font-semibold text-purple-900 mb-2">Brand Building Payoff</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Long-term brand investments take 12-24 months to show full returns—but most CMOs don't have that patience</p>
        </div>
      </div>

